---
title: Sweet-Soy Tofu & Greens Poke Bowl with Japanese Dressing & Pickled Cucumber
description: We love poke bowls because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This veggie version uses marinated tofu, Asian greens and cucumber, with a Japanese dressing to tie the whole thing together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
